{"tid":1914433,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突發】：隔離患者酒店倒塌 70人被活埋","createTime":"2020-03-07T13:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T08:47:58.000Z","uid":150145,"like":479,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":119,"replies":[{"pid":"aea45a3f4cf8341ebc5103f634811fb0f5c6b206","tid":1914433,"uid":150145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q9uDg27.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ9uDg27.gif&h=6008c90c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFKing泉州鯉城區周六（7日）一幢5層高的酒店突然倒塌，目前70人被困，至少已救出23人。據內媒報道指，上址是新冠肺炎患者的隔離點。<br />\n事發於鯉城區南環路，由現場圖片可見，酒店整幢大廈完全倒塌，現場一片混亂，救援人員在瓦礫中搜救傷者。<br />\n據住在倒塌酒店對面屋苑的吳姓目擊者稱，倒塌的酒店名為欣佳酒店。事發時他正在吃飯，突然聽到一聲巨響，還以為是爆炸。他還稱，在現場看到很多救護車和消防車趕來救援，也親眼見到救援人員將傷者背出廢墟。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E5%80%92%E5%A1%8C-%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E6%B4%BB%E5%9F%8B%E5%9C%A8%E7%93%A6%E7%A4%AB%E5%A0%86%E4%B8%AD-132353081.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A2%25E6%2582%25A3%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%25BA%2597%25E5%2580%2592%25E5%25A1%258C-%25E5%25A4%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%259F%258B%25E5%259C%25A8%25E7%2593%25A6%25E7%25A4%25AB%25E5%25A0%2586%25E4%25B8%25AD-132353081.html&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuJ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=830c81eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E5%80%92%E5%A1%8C-%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E6%B4%BB%E5%9F%8B%E5%9C%A8%E7%93%A6%E7%A4%AB%E5%A0%86%E4%B8%AD-132353081.html</a>"},{"pid":"7ab3bc9c0b122a0bc95befd12107fda0f369a993","tid":1914433,"uid":177089,"like":208,"dislike":3,"score":205,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:44:22.000Z","msg":"撲滅病患"},{"pid":"25f305a3e50424bf71b6a0da19447d34359c4bd4